OL,3,CThe 'money-saving' asylum seeker plan
OL,4,Ccosting taxpayer #46m extra
OL,6,FBut today, the National Audit Office
OL,7,F(NAO) proved that the claim its
OL,8,Falternative plan would save money was
OL,9,Fincorrect.
OL,11,FIn reality, these mass accommodation
OL,12,Fsites will cost more than hotels -
OL,13,Fabout #46 million more, according to
OL,14,Fthe NAO.
OL,16,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,17,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,18,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,19,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/13
