OL,3,CThe 'money-saving' asylum seeker plan
OL,4,Ccosting taxpayer #46m extra
OL,6,FAnother mass accommodation site in
OL,7,FHuddersfield was initially expected to
OL,8,Fsave #23million, but will in fact cost
OL,9,F#2million more than using hotels.
OL,11,F#2.9million spent on a third site in
OL,12,Four region - the former RAF base at
OL,13,FLinton-on-Ouse - has been lost, after
OL,14,Fthe project got cancelled.
OL,16,FGiven the controversy that has plagued
OL,17,Fthe Government's plans for sites like
OL,18,FScampton from the start, the NAO's
OL,19,Freport presents a pretty damning
OL,20,Fpicture.
