OL,3,CThe 'money-saving' asylum seeker plan
OL,4,Ccosting taxpayer #46m extra
OL,6,FAnd, it turns out, that's only the
OL,7,Fbest case scenario.
OL,9,FThe report is based on the Home
OL,10,FOffice's costings for filling mass
OL,11,Fasylum sites to their maximum capacity.
OL,13,FBut those capacities are now being
OL,14,Freconsidered.
OL,16,FRAF Scampton was initially supposed to
OL,17,Fhouse 2,000 asylum seekers, but that's
OL,19,FAs the NAO report acknowledges,
OL,20,Fthat'll make the cost-benefit analysis
OL,21,Feven more dire.
