OL,3,CThe 'money-saving' asylum seeker plan
OL,4,Ccosting taxpayer #46m extra
OL,6,FHousing migrants in a barge like the
OL,7,FBibby Stockholm, or on a former
OL,8,Fmilitary base, makes the Government
OL,9,Fmight look tougher in the eyes of some
OL,10,F- but if it costs more, it's difficult
OL,11,Fto justify.
OL,13,FIn response to the report, the
OL,14,FGovernment has doubled down on its
OL,15,Fasylum centre plan will save money.
