OL,3,CThe 'money-saving' asylum seeker plan
OL,4,Ccosting taxpayer #46m extra
OL,6,FA Home Office spokesperson also told
OL,7,Fus: "We are passing the Safety of
OL,8,FRwanda Bill, deterring Channel
OL,9,Fcrossings and get flights off to
OL,10,FRwanda - because it is only when
OL,11,Fpeople are discouraged from taking
OL,12,Fthose journeys that we can end asylum
OL,13,Fhotel use for good."
OL,15,FThe Rwanda plan is currently stuck in
OL,16,Fa ping-pong match between the House of
OL,17,FLords and the House of Commons, but
OL,18,Fthe Government hopes it'll deter
OL,19,Fmigrants from coming to the UK.
