OL,6,FBy the Government's own assessment,
OL,7,Fthough, the plan would need to deter
OL,8,F37% of people who would otherwise have
OL,9,Farrived in the UK, just to break even.
OL,11,F"Stop the Boats" is one of Rishi
OL,12,FSunak's five priorities - something
OL,13,Fhe's promised the public again and
OL,14,Fagain.
OL,16,FHe may find his Government lives or
OL,17,Fdies by the success of that pledge.
